                "invention-title": [
                    "System and method for purifying high-purity hydrogen by coupling catalysis and metal hydrogen storage alloy",
                    "催化与金属储氢合金耦合纯化高纯氢气的系统和方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a system and method for purifying high-purity hydrogen through catalysis and metal hydrogen storage alloy coupling, and the method comprises the following steps: CO-containing high-purity hydrogen enters a catalysis unit, and CO in the raw material is converted into carbon dioxide and/or methane; intermediate product gas is obtained; the intermediate product gas optionally enters the heat exchange unit and/or the adsorption unit and then enters the metal hydrogen storage alloy unit, and hydrogen in the product gas is absorbed and impurity gas is removed. According to the invention, the first catalytic unit is mainly used for removing CO in the raw material gas and converting CO into CO2 or CH4 gas with relatively high tolerance to the metal hydrogen storage alloy, CO2 and H2O adsorbents can be introduced after catalysis when the CO content is high, the CO is removed to a relatively low concentration, then the gas enters the metal hydrogen storage purification unit, the metal hydrogen storage alloy in the unit only absorbs hydrogen, and the metal hydrogen storage alloy in the unit only absorbs hydrogen; other impurity components are removed, and finally high-purity hydrogen is produced. The novel process can significantly improve the hydrogen recovery rate and reduce the hydrogen purification cost for the fuel cell vehicle."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种催化与金属储氢合金耦合纯化高纯氢气的系统和方法，该方法包括：含CO的高纯氢气进入催化单元，所述原料中的CO转化为二氧化碳和/或甲烷；获得中间产品气；所述中间产品气可选地进入换热单元和/或吸附单元后进入金属储氢合金单元，产品气中的氢气被吸收杂质气被去除。本发明，主要利用第一个催化单元重点脱除原料气中CO，将CO转化成对金属储氢合金容忍度较高的CO2或CH4气体，在高CO含量时可以在催化后接CO2及H2O吸附剂，将其脱除至较低浓度然后气体进入金属储氢纯化单元，在该单元金属储氢合金仅吸收氢气，其它杂质组分被去除，最终生产出高纯度氢气。该新型工艺可显著提高氢气回收率，降低燃料电池车用氢气纯化成本。"
                }
            ]
